<td width="60%">
<p><strong>Gaddiel Hawki Android Mobile App</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">The goal of this App is to track the movement of registered mobiles through SMS at a user configurable time interval.  It also has the facility to send an SMS to get the current location of the mobile immediately.  All the configurations and accesses by User are handled in the Mobile App.</p>
