<table>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td width="60%">
<p><strong>Jindal Gaddiel Hawki Android Mobile App</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">This mobile app caters to Customer Relationship Management and Reporting requirements. The data captured is real-time. The real time data is shared across the management team for follow-up on the customer requirements. Further the travel efficiency and compliance to Standard Operating Procedures and Processes are tracked. This helps in analyzing the efficiency of the employees while at the same time improves the customer satisfaction.</p>
<object class="mobile-view" data="https://www.youtube.com/embed/S5D-wK07Czg"></object></td>
