<td width="60%">
<p><strong>Reflective Rosary (English), (Tamil), (Malayalam)</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">A Mobile App that helps RC in their prayer. Available on Google Play.  The Mobile App, (English version) helps user to record the prayers in their favourite voice.  The prayer can be played on schedule or as and when one wishes. The display language and the schedules are configurable. These apps have been downloaded across the Globe. </p>
<a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.gaddiel.holyrosary" target="_blank">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.gaddiel.holyrosary</a> <br /> <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.gaddiel.tamilrosary" target="_blank">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.gaddiel.tamilrosary</a><br /> <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=gaddiel.malayalamrosary" target="_blank">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=gaddiel.malayalamrosary</a><object class="mobile-view" data="https://www.youtube.com/embed/KZNslApq2y0"></object></td>
