<tbody>
<tr>
<td width="60%">
<p><strong>Android NFC/QR Data capturing Mobile App </strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">This Product is under development. This product enables the shop floor level supervisors to intelligently capture real-time production data of any machine/ machinist.  The App is so intuitive that users have to only click or select the context sensitive options shown on the screen.  The learning curve is fast and utilization can be very effective.  The real-time data captured is sent to production management team for pro-active steps to meet the targets or reduce wastage of time, labour and material.</p>
